    Observer<java.lang.Integer>, UpdateStrategy<java.lang.Integer>

    public class WaitingForChunksObserver
extends AbstractObserver<java.lang.Integer>
    This class emits an event when chunks we are creating or retrieving from a Black Pearl are not yet available. The event reports the number of seconds we will wait before trying again.
